General.Name: Banco di Desio e della Brianza S.p.A
General.Description: Banco di Desio e della Brianza S.p.A. provides banking products and services to individuals and enterprises in Italy. The company offers current and deposit accounts, mortgages, personal loans and financing, and car and life insurance products. It also provides financial, Internet and mobile banking, electronic payment, documentary credit, leasing, factoring, and asset management products and services; investment, protection, and retirement products; and debit and credit cards. The company was incorporated in 1909 and is based in Desio, Italy. Banco di Desio e della Brianza S.p.A. Banco di Desio e della Brianza S.p.A. is a subsidiary of Brianza Unione di Luigi Gavazzi e Stefano Lado S.A.p.A.
